response.original_title: NJPW Presents CMLL Fantastica Mania 2017: Day 6
response.overview: On January 21, 2017, NJPW Presents CMLL Fantastica Mania 2017 held its Day 6 event at Tokyo's Korakuen Hall, broadcast on Samurai! TV. The main attraction was a World Heavyweight Title Match featuring Maximo Sexy against Hechicero. Another notable encounter saw Euforia and Ultimo Guerrero face off against Mistico and Volador Jr. in a Tag Team Match. Other wrestlers on the show include Kazuchika Okada, Will Ospreay, Rush, and Atlantis, and more!
response.title: NJPW Presents CMLL Fantastica Mania 2017: Day 6
